releaseNotes:
We love hearing from our customers and we work quickly to resolve any bugs reported by you in our quest to make the best mental health app on the App Store. Because of your feedback and reviews, this update fixes a bug that caused Wellness Mini to crash when adding a note on Apple Watch. Also, you can now edit a mood entry even if it doesn't have a note attached.

We're currently working on a big new update to Wellness and we're really excited to be the first and only app on the App Store with this type of feature.

Reviews are super-duper critical to help us build new features and improvements for Wellness. If you haven't done so already, please take a minute to leave a review.

For technical support, general questions, feedback and feature requests, you can reach us directly inside of Wellness. Just open Wellness > Settings > Customer Support and you'll be chatting with us (the real, human makers of Wellness)!

Thank you for using Wellness
description:
Wellness is a mood, medication, and health journal that helps you understand your mental health.

* Quickly track moods and see your mood charted over time from your iPhone or Apple Watch
* Set up reminders to take your medications or vitamins, and see how consistently you take them
* Integrate with Apple Health to see your health data in one place
* Secure your data with your passcode and Touch ID or Face ID

# Always know how you've been feeling
With Wellness, you'll always have the data to describe how you've been feeling. The mood chart shows your  moods over time, so you can see every change in your mood — big or small.

# Understand your medication use
Some medications help, some don't. Wellness knows when you plan to take your medication and remembers when you haven't, painting a clearer picture of your adherence.

# Private and secured with your touch
Your mood, medication, and health history is sensitive information. You can always secure your data in Wellness with Face ID or Touch ID and a passcode.

—————————

**Wellness is always free to use to track your mood cycles.** 

Pillbox and Health integration features will require Wellness to be unlocked. All Wellness features are unlocked for the first 7 days. After that, you will have the following Wellness Unlock options:

Mood tracking only:
- Wellness Basic: FREE

All Features Unlocked:
- Wellness Monthly: $5 per month
- Wellness Forever: $50 once


• Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase
• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period
• Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal
• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase
• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable
